    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Materials that are used for smoking, often processed or made into a certain forms, such as cigars or cigarettes that are contain or are made of tobacco. Smoking materials are typically used for recreation or for medicinal purposes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
